widgets_values:
Here, we define variables that will be reused during the generation in all scenes.

It includes the main character, clothes, the rendering style and the environment.

You can set parameters to your liking by clicking on a node to unfold it.

You can also change seed of one element or even re-generate all prompts.

This way, you can precisely define what parts you want to be random. For even more control, you can also use a `{variable}` name in the prompt
